Who knows?

237
00:18:20,699 --> 00:18:27,730
She's always pleasant, and I can't
tell you how annoying that is.

238
00:18:27,840 --> 00:18:32,903
Whatever she feels,
it's so far below the surface...

239
00:18:42,154 --> 00:18:44,247
Bree?

240
00:18:45,691 --> 00:18:49,889
- Bree?
- What? I'm sorry.

241
00:18:49,962 --> 00:18:53,523
Would you like to respond
to what Rex just said?

242
00:18:53,632 --> 00:18:57,261
- Oh, um...
- Is there some truth there?

243
00:18:57,369 --> 00:19:02,773
Do you use housework as a way
to disengage emotionally?

244
00:19:02,875 --> 00:19:04,433
Of course not!

245
00:19:07,112 --> 00:19:11,947
This is great.
I got tons of homework tonight.

246
00:19:12,050 --> 00:19:15,247
- It's easy to concentrate after sex.
- I'm glad I could help.

247
00:19:15,320 --> 00:19:17,254
Education's very important.

248
00:19:17,356 --> 00:19:20,257
Oh, I got something for you.

249
00:19:20,359 --> 00:19:24,523
