250
00:19:27,166 --> 00:19:30,033
- Oh, it's a rose.
- It's not just any rose.

251
00:19:30,169 --> 00:19:32,637
Look at all the petals.
There's no flaws.

252
00:19:32,704 --> 00:19:35,673
- It's perfect.
- Oh, John.

253
00:19:36,508 --> 00:19:37,941
Just like you.

254
00:19:38,010 --> 00:19:40,308
The truth hit her like a thunderbolt.

255
00:19:40,412 --> 00:19:44,246
I spent days looking for
just the right one. I finally found it.

256
00:19:44,316 --> 00:19:48,252
For John, this was no longer
a meaningless little affair.

257
00:19:48,353 --> 00:19:52,756
Gabrielle could now clearly se
he was falling in love with her.

258
00:19:52,824 --> 00:19:54,985
It's just beautiful.

259
00:19:57,496 --> 00:20:00,659
I... I got to go.

260
00:20:04,036 --> 00:20:05,264
Goodbye.

261
00:20:09,808 --> 00:20:13,676
Hey, you. What are we having?

262
00:20:13,779 --> 00:20:18,011
