but was powerless to stop it.

279
00:21:16,375 --> 00:21:18,366
Would you like
to join us for dinner?

280
00:21:18,477 --> 00:21:23,938
Oh, that's so sweet. No, I don't want
to intrude. Three's a crowd.

281
00:21:24,049 --> 00:21:28,281
