I mean, Susan's bringing Julie.

282
00:21:28,353 --> 00:21:31,618
It's not like that.
The more the merrier.

283
00:21:31,690 --> 00:21:35,148
- Well, this'll be fun.
- All right. Tomorrow night.

284
00:21:35,227 --> 00:21:37,354
- We'll eat at six.
- Great.

285
00:21:38,563 --> 00:21:40,292
