287
00:21:43,902 --> 00:21:45,631
Right.

288
00:21:45,704 --> 00:21:47,137
Ta-ta.

289
00:21:47,205 --> 00:21:51,369
Should I have told her we were having
steak. She's not a vegetarian?

290
00:21:51,443 --> 00:21:54,276
Oh, no, no.

291
00:21:54,379 --> 00:21:58,315
No, Edie's definitely a carnivore.

292
00:22:02,587 --> 00:22:03,747
- Here's, um...
- Ooh.

293
00:22:03,822 --> 00:22:05,449
Here's what I pulled for Edie.

294
00:22:05,557 --> 00:22:08,617
